Name: Couple in Trouble
About the game: Challenge yourself in a world of obstacles and dangers, test your skills in a fun and challenging game. Use teamwork to guide the characters through each stage. Press levers, dodge bombs, spikes and poisonous gases to move forward together. Featuring 35 levels created by hand with increasing complexity. A fun 2D platform puzzle.
